Class Gibbot

  • java.lang.Object
    • Gibbot

  • public class Gibbot
extends java.lang.Object
    A Gibbot object contains data on where the robot is on the board, to be translated to user interface. Right now its method for updating its own animation is a simulation, but a commented outline is above it for hypothetically getting the real coordinates from GUISerialPort, which also contains a dummy method now. All the get methods may not be neccessary (last four are currently unused) but they were left just in case.
